Step 1. Create The Bucket

Download The Zip File neogym-html.zip

Login AWS Console -> Search Bar -> S3 -> Create bucket -> Bucket name -> Uncheck The Block all public access And Acknowledged -> Create bucket


Step 2. Create The Bucket Policy

Select The Bucket -> Permissions -> Bucket policy -> Edit -> Copy And Paste The Bucket-Policy -> Save changes


Step 3. Enable The Static website hosting

Select The Bucket -> Properties -> Static website hosting -> Edit -> Enable -> Index document (index.html) -> Save changes -> Upload All Website Files And Folders

